member.name: M:Enderlook.Unity.Utils.IPrototypable`1.CreatePrototype
member.summary:
Uses instance as "template" to create new instances of the same class.
It's not full deep clone, but rather a clone of only the necessary values to make a new instance.
All other values are left as default.
This method is useful to use an instance as a template to make new instances of it.
member.returns: New instance based of template instance.
